{"tid":992994,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)羅賓漢 移動城市","createTime":"2019-01-23T14:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T17:11:37.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"367c144ca7d11c5ff3d743a9160b96a75ab917da","tid":992994,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:42:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=0%2FqHyhg9rghSYbtahiOo6Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=47ac0c06\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=0%2FqHyhg9rghSYbtahiOo6Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=d193419f\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=0%2FqHyhg9rghSYbtahiOo6Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=bca85a02\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e7/Robin_Hood_2018_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe7%2FRobin_Hood_2018_Poster.jpg&h=24524d59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/62/Mortal_Engines_%28film%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F62%2FMortal_Engines_%2528film%2529.jpg&h=551509d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.英勇的羅賓漢（泰隆艾格頓 飾）在成為劫富濟貧的義賊之前，是諾丁漢中的貴族拉克斯里羅伯，他接受治安官(班曼德森 飾演)的強制徵招參加十字軍東征，與信奉回教的阿拉伯人爭戰，在他目睹十字軍對戰俘的殘酷行為後，他回到家鄉，本以為能安穩度日，卻目睹在治安官的暴政統治下，社會充斥犯罪和酷吏，人民在政府暴行下叫苦連天。為了找回和平，羅賓漢聯手正義的夥伴，試圖對抗這群暴虐、腐敗的官吏和貴族，重建美麗家園<br />\n<br />\n2.21世紀歷經六十分鐘戰爭後，世界就此毀於一旦。然而殘存的文化與技術，一千年後發展為裝載巨輪的移動城市在殘酷的未來世界中，它們互相獵食彼此，至死方休。倫敦城低階的16歲歷史學家湯姆一直以來都待在自己的家鄉，他的腳從未接觸過草地、泥土和大地，對身邊的事只略知一二。某日，湯姆阻止了企圖暗殺薩杜斯&middot;瓦倫丁的蒙面女性海絲特&middot;蕭，她聲稱要為自己死去的母親復仇，但這也使得海絲特和湯姆最終被這座移動的「牽引」大城，放任他們自生自滅，故事便在此處開始了他們的旅程⋯<br />\n<br />\n11 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 北韓流出版<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=0%2FqHyhg9rghSYbtahiOo6Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=a27d410a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=0%2FqHyhg9rghSYbtahiOo6Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=14443bb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e440071c62993fbba79e5620aa1a873daaad2b","tid":992994,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de14743912c94b6e71e65e37c029ec802a7db44","tid":992994,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face